  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK646">
<l>vēṭpattāñ collip piṟarcoṟpayaṉkōṭaṉ </l>
<l> māṭciyiṉ mācaṟṟār kōḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the opinion of those who are free from defects in diplomacy that the minister should speak so as to make his hearers desire (to hear more) and grasp the meaning of what he hears himself.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
